{"tid":2260318,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"停課影響 青少年最苦惱","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:26:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62a3b1f11fc814213fd3c40dbf759e3699530041","tid":2260318,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/LDNZPG4NJRCKPGOUVUN3TL5NKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FLDNZPG4NJRCKPGOUVUN3TL5NKA%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDEqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=593ff8ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FLDNZPG4NJRCKPGOUVUN3TL5NKA%2F&h=f15dd052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/LDNZPG4NJRCKPGOUVUN3TL5NKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n停課影響 青少年最苦惱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jnu92BIKGC1LOfXkLAnh8DNLGkk=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DMT7CQE5VRBHZF7SV5NV4UUETY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJnu92BIKGC1LOfXkLAnh8DNLGkk%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDMT7CQE5VRBHZF7SV5NV4UUETY.jpg&h=b05c7bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「香港開心D」發表2020年港人開心指數。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港人不開心，12至18歲的受訪者更是六個年齡群組中最不開心的一群，開心指數由去年的6.2分大跌至5.87分；另一個錄得跌幅的年齡層是45至54歲群組，跌幅為0.14個百分點。去年最不開心的25至34歲群組今年開心指數升幅較為顯注，由5.92分回升至6.21分，增加0.29個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭施政不堪 港人持續不開心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港男首次開心過港女<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現年齡越細越不開心，年齡群組按不開心程度排序為12至18歲（5.87分）、19至24歲（6.03分）、45至54歲（6.18分）、25至34歲（6.21分）、35至44歲（6.28分）及55歲或以上（6.61分），即只有45至54歲群組不符趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n港女今年亦首次比港男不開心，港女開心指數按年由6.22分跌至6.1分，港男則由6.07分升至6.24分，兩性快樂度相差0.14個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n教育野發言人鄭家朗表示，國。。。。。。。。。。。，故快樂指數低。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f93d31a8dc11034de2d0245fc5f4c001322cb4ae","tid":2260318,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"Can&rsquo;t see 女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aefd95b95e8dbb349bf0600767a9bd2e8ae88e","tid":2260318,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANGr2GX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGr2GX.png&h=017d56af&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}